betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Getting by and finding comfort in this land is hard.
And yet, it can be done, to an extent.
I am happy that, even in my most vulnerable state, I was able of getting back on my feet.
Sure, what I do may still lead to failure, but I was capable of standing up.
The help I received may still go to waste, but I was capable of standing up.
The sacrifice may be too much, but I was capable of standing up.
And they cannot take that away from me!
